{"tid":724594,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得係呢個年代既球迷好可惜？冇機會睇到球皇登基","createTime":"2018-07-01T05:03:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-01T05:10:17.000Z","uid":43770,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8dfcfa1d38741599178b22897a883d14fdd07416","tid":724594,"uid":43770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:03:39.000Z","msg":"無論籃波定足球都係咁，球員實力就算真係勁過上一代球王都比人踩低。<br />\n<br />\n籃波：占士唔洗講，得三冠冇得同高比/MJ比<br />\n咖哩仔，73勝全票MVP，差一步封神。點知3-1總決賽但底線傷/停反敗，係連燈仔面前一世抬唔起頭<br />\n<br />\n足球：冇世盃點樣同老馬比利比較，甚至廢過拖丹大細哨<br />\nC朗：國家隊隊友堅唔係一線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美斯：隊友一線，但把握唔到。有張2014世盃決賽後既相望住大力神盃真係令人感到好唏噓<br />\n<br />\n老實講佢地成就毋庸置疑，但呢啲小小遺憾令佢地生涯變得唔完美。可能佢地都睇化，但作為球迷好想見到呢一代有球王誕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f441730228e98ad2980955e89fead835b14fcf0","tid":724594,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"美欺14年世界盃錯失封神機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a663780e2677438aef8bea9811eed8c767439c73","tid":724594,"uid":43770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T05:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/01/131015_fd2f7b7d5b6d05febc8e0935380921c3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F01%2F131015_fd2f7b7d5b6d05febc8e0935380921c3.png&h=c0cf69f1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}